data.description: One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, Pub Quiz covers topics including geography, history, sports, celebrities, and everything in between. We highly recommend using this in your first game of Outsmarted!

One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, Back 2 School will transport you like a time machine back to those dreaded chemistry, physics, biology, math, English, history, and geography classes! Totally unique to Outsmarted, we recommend using this in your first game!

One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, our Quick Thinking category includes brainteasers, anagrams, riddles, and pattern recognition, this is certain to cause some arguments! Totally unique to Outsmarted and a LOT of fun, we suggest using this in your first game of Outsmarted!

One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, our Sound & Music category covers all things music from decades past & present, and is sure to be a hit (pun intended). We recommend using this in your first game of Outsmarted!

One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, our TV, Film & Books category features iconic film stills, TV series stills and celebrity pics! We cover all the films you would have rented at Blockbuster, right through to the TV series you're currently watching on Netflix! We highly recommend using this in your first game of Outsmarted!

One of the six Outsmarted Core Pack categories, our Breaking News category is perhaps our coolest. Updated every single week - and sometimes every day - it's packed with questions on local and global news: get ready to put all those news reading hours to good use! Sports, entertainment, politics, offbeat, music, business, tech... if it's in the news, it might be here!

Whether you fell in love with The Persistence of Memory at the MoMA, or The Last Supper in Milan, with everything from impressionism, surrealism, pop art and more, this is packed full of your favourite artists, both past & present, with every question featuring the artwork itself!

This category is packed full of global sports trivia, covering sporting events & sports personalities, with iconic sporting images on EVERY SINGLE question!
